 don''t do that, it won''t matter how clever your business model is.', 2095, 0), (425834, 'In every business, in every industry, management does matter.', 38689, 0), (425835, 'You have to respect your parents. They are giving you an at-bat. If you''re an entrepreneur and go into the family business, you want to grow fast. Patience is important. But respect the other party... My dad and I pulled it off because we really respect each other.', 11355, 0), (425836, 'The most important quality in a leader is that of being acknowledged as such. All leaders whose fitness is questioned are clearly lacking in force.', 10019, 0), (425837, 'Business is a combination of war and sport.', 10019, 0), (425838, 'To command is to serve, nothing more and nothing less.', 38147, 0), (425839, 'The leader who exercises power with honor will work from the inside out, starting with himself.', 66740, 0), (425840, 'The business of America is business.', 4110, 0), (425841, 'The consumer isn''t a moron she is your wife. ', 17061, 0), (425842, 'If it doesn''t sell, it isn''t creative.', 17061, 0), (425843, 'The characteristic of great innovators and great companies is they see a space that others do not. They don''t just listen to what people tell them; they actually invent something new, something that you didn''t know you needed, but the moment you see it, you say, ''I must have it.''', 4910, 0), (425844, 'Spend a lot of time talking to customers face to face. You''d be amazed how many companies don''t listen to their customers.', 66580, 0), (425845, 'I''m not a driven businessman, but a driven artist. I never think about money. Beautiful things make money.', 63500, 0), (425846, 'I don''t think meals have any business being deductible. I''m for separation of calories and corporations.', 23125, 0), (425847, 'Every few seconds it changes - up an eighth, down an eighth - it''s like playing a slot machine. I lose $20 million, I gain $20 million.', 34846, 0), (425848, 'If you aren''t playing well, the game isn''t as much fun. When that happens I tell myself just to go out and play as I did when I was a kid.', 63121, 0), (425849, 'Whenever an individual or a business decides that success has been attained, progress stops.', 63121, 0), (425850, 'Web users ultimately want to get at data quickly and easily. They don''t care as much about attractive sites and pretty design.', 59325, 0);
